CROWD [CHANTING]:
United! We'll never be defeated!

01:14.616 --> 01:17.483
[CROWD YELLING]

01:17.703 --> 01:19.785
MAN [VOICE DISTORTED]:
The storm has come.

01:19.997 --> 01:22.363
A wave of death and destruction,

01:22.583 --> 01:25.700
aimed at the few
who've left so little for so many.

01:26.378 --> 01:27.993
It will wash away the greedy,

01:28.213 --> 01:32.172
and when it does,
you can thank General Ludd.

01:33.176 --> 01:34.791
[m1

01:34.970 --> 01:36.961
[WATER RUNNING]

01:40.267 --> 01:41.677
What are you still doing here?

01:41.893 --> 01:45.806
Hey, late start. Teacher in-service.
I'm supposed to bring donuts

01:46.023 --> 01:49.231
as if Mrs. Wempon's ass
could use another bear claw.

01:49.401 --> 01:50.811
RAUGHS]

01:51.987 --> 01:54.603
What's going on here?
You know.

01:54.823 --> 01:58.156
Good morning.
I'm working on it.

01:58.368 --> 02:05.206
